<br>
For 3 years they have not asked me to pay more.  That's more than I can say for gas stations, grocery stores, landlords and college.  <br>
<br>
The cost of living in California is insane and the GMs do not get paid small fortunes.  With the electricity issues they have out there, can you imagine how much their electric bill is each month?  <br>
<br>
For 10 dollars or 13 dollars....I still get all the playtime I want (minus patches) for my money.  It's cheaper than going to the movies with a friend once a month.  Cheaper than a dinner somewhere other than McDonald's.  <br>
<br>
Since the beginning of the game people have cried foul at Verant...but they keep coming back.  I've said it before and I'll say it again.  If you actually knew what it took to run an operation of the magnitude such as EQ, you might just realize how smoothly it actually runs.  <br>
